comments.author: jacafbiz
comments.body: Good for the project to be able to raise funds and from some of the heavyweights in the space, the concern I have is the adoption of the SUI network itself, I feel it is unwise for any project to decide to be native to any chain now, look at Pancake and Uniswap they have both moved out of their native chains and expand into other chains, if this project wants to have a grip of the market and gain market share I will advise that it moves to other networks
